  • Classes in tatami.core.agent used by tatami.core.agent 
    Class and Description
    AgentComponent
    This class serves as base for agent component.
    AgentComponent.AgentComponentName
    Enumeration of available component names / functionalities.
    AgentEvent
    The class stores an agent event, characterized by its type and, optionally, a set of parameters that have names.
    AgentEvent.AgentEventType
    The enumeration specified the full set of agent-internal events that can occur.
    AgentEvent.AgentSequenceType
    The sequence type of an agent event specifies the order in which components should be notified of the event.
    CompositeAgent
    This class reunites the components of an agent in order for components to be able to call each other and for events to be distributed to all components.
